**Working hours:**
- {{GetCustomerAttribute(field="project_attributes_private_dynamic_schedule_working_hours")}}

# Exceptions
**Schedule exceptions:**
- {{#if not IsEmpty(text=working_days_hours_exceptions)}}{{working_days_hours_exceptions}}{{else}}no exceptions{{/if}}
</WorkingSchedule>

